reviews.review_text: a Great show A friend of mine recommended this show as one I should listen to.  Much to my surprise it had been recorded by Charlie Miller, whom I had patched into for half a dozen Phil shows a decade later.  Those Nak shotgun mikes are great for recording. a great show with great sound quality.
